ActBroadcasting Act
SubjectCanadian Broadcasting Corporation **LEASING OF PROPERTY**
PrecisOrder authorizing the Canadian Broadcasting Corporation to enter into a lease agreement with UKEN STUDIOS INC. as tenant to lease a portion of the real property at 250 Front Street West in Toronto, Ontario, and to grant in favor of UKEN STUDIOS INC., an option to renew the lease for two further periods of five years.
